Barbara, Gelarent, Darii, Ferio, Baralipet, dolantes, Debitio, Fapesmo‚ Frisesmo‚ deinde (lesere, (lamestres, Festino, Barooo‚ Darapti‚ Felapton‚ Disamia Datisi, Booardo, Ferison.
